3.1.0-beta.2
============

* All numbers between -12 and 12 are now considered "small", and preserved
  in the sentence without replacing with NUMBER tokens [#33]
* Misc bug fixes [#31, #32]

3.1.0-beta.1
============

* Added support for Italian [#24, #29]
* Update official builds to Java 11, as Java 8 is obsolete [#30]

3.0.3
=====

* Fixed tokenization of dates

3.0.2
=====

* Improved tokenization of zip codes and numbers connected to a word with a -
  (e.g. "5-star")

3.0.1
=====

* Removed unused functionality and dependencies [#25]
* Added official docker build instructions [#26]

3.0.0
=====

* First tagged release of almond-tokenizer

The version number starts at 3.0.0 to avoid conflicts with SEMPRE, which
is part of the history of this codebase and uses versions 1.* and 2.*.
